      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>C基础</h1><p>作者：L（knock_s@foxmial.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="变量">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f"></a>
变量
</h2><p>标识符（变量名）命名规则：</p>
<p>​	1.不能是关键字</p>
<p>​	2.只能由字母数字下划线组成</p>
<p>​	3.字母区分大小写</p>
<p>​	4.第一个字符只能是字母或下划线</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-c" data-lang="c"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="err">\\定义变量，占用内存空间</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">========================================</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">extern</span> <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="err">\\</span> <span class="err">声明变量，不占用内存</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="p">;</span> <span class="c1">//会发生报错。
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// extern也叫类型限定符。
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="类型限定符">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%b1%bb%e5%9e%8b%e9%99%90%e5%ae%9a%e7%ac%a6"></a>
类型限定符
</h3><ul>
<li>extern</li>
<li>const</li>
<li>register</li>
<li>volatile</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="常量">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%b8%b8%e9%87%8f"></a>
常量
</h2><ul>
<li>宏常量</li>
</ul>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-C" data-lang="C"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// #defind 常量名 初始值
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">#define HP 100
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><p>​</p>
        
